      <title>斯里兰卡债券持有人计划本月进行新一轮债务谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/sri-lanka-bondholders-plan-fresh-round-of-debt-talks-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，全球投资者和斯里兰卡官员预计将于本月晚些时候举行第二轮谈判，旨在重组 120 亿美元违约的全球债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/sri-lanka-bondholders-plan-fresh-round-of-debt-talks-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
